We'd like something can be used as a square image both for app buttons/icons and social media, and that won't be too complicated for a 40x40 pixel image.

My elevator pitch: "I help women who are chronic overdoers shift from hesitant to Hell YES! so they can bring their vision to life!"
My clients are capable, creative, women who have spent their careers helping others achieve their goals, dreams, and visions - which has left little energy to dream their own dream or listen to their own desires (their YES!). I help them learn to listen to that voice within and nurture it until they come to want to focus and tend to their own dream/vision. That is what I do.
Target audience - Women ages 28 - 55, have careers or their own businesses. INcome $50K+/yr.
Likely over committed - committees, PTO, Super Mom, trying to do it all. Managing, controlling from the sidelines
Seeking inspiration, validation, a solution to finding her own voice/path/value
Frustrated by feeling jealous of others success, not knowing HOW to achieve her dreams, not knowing HOW to dream for her self.
Wants - a clear path, a vision for herself, practical steps to get there, and support and help along the way, mostly she wants to show up for herself the way she shows up for others.
other_notes:
I want to share my background about the business name - Yesward Coaching LLC. Yes is the cornerstone of the work that I do, the attitude and energy I bring, and the core of my faith. I am a very spiritual (not religious) person - I don't believe in purpose but I do believe that each of us has a desire that guides what we want to be and create in the world - I call that our YES. I also believe that the answer from God/The Universe/ The All that Is/Allah (whatever flavor) is YES - it is the energy of life force, and growth and expansion. So, when I selected Yesward Coaching - it is about moving in the direction of YES (Yesward - like Northward/Southward) and when we do this we are always on the right path. When we honor that YES, we experience a feeling of purpose, value, and power- which increases our confidence and willingness to respond with a RESOUNDING YES! I thought this might help - I love the NAME and I find it inspiring - I want a logo that captures the essence of this.
My personality - I am fun, bold, lighthearted but direct, I am colorful, lively - I am not the typical woo-woo incense and Chakra gal - I am Just One Woo and I take a very practical approach to support my clients in becoming their best selves.
I am looking for a UNIQUE logo. Something that is not typical or expected.
Why a new logo for my new business- I want to focus more on Coaching, Public Speaking, Teaching and Personal Transformation, bringing forward more energy of Professionalism, Expertise, and Wisdom. I want to OWN the word and the energy of YES!
I look forward to what you have to share.
